{"tid":2508561,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"為應對中國威脅 歐盟擬訂新規例限制外資活動","createTime":"2021-04-29T00:40:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-29T00:59:16.000Z","uid":396114,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7d1fff6c5ac8426efe0c9d73184f6eb9bf3adbee","tid":2508561,"uid":396114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T00:40:12.000Z","msg":"外電報道，歐盟委員會正擬制訂新法案，以制止外國政府支持的國企大肆併購歐洲企業，並對違規企業處以罰款或禁止進行交易。有關法案被視為面對中國經濟威脅而作出的應對行動。<br />\n<a href=\"https://plus01media.com/finance/20210429/european-union-proposed-law-prevent-foreign-capital\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplus01media.com%2Ffinance%2F20210429%2Feuropean-union-proposed-law-prevent-foreign-capital&d=DgCTbN7XbHZJJfbPUwNNzWo8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=8e9a5c82\" target=\"_blank\">https://plus01media.com/finance/20210429/european-union-proposed-law-prevent-foreign-capital</a><br />\n華為呢d中資企 冇左共產黨補貼死硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c59c12162691a70053261d25805cab3268dd82cb","tid":2508561,"uid":52828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T00:45:15.000Z","msg":"要加埋已被共產黨收購嘅外國企業唔俾再揼水落去咁先有效喎，如果唔係，一樣有其他方法俾共產黨收購。"},{"pid":"3383a1ccae4f894ea557e9711575a6998d7b438a","tid":2508561,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T00:47:43.000Z","msg":"一早要"},{"pid":"579ffe0d24f442f9376972880dd7de31c838e0c5","tid":2508561,"uid":396114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3383a1ccae4f894ea557e9711575a6998d7b438a","tid":2508561,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T00:47:43.000Z","msg":"一早要"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T00:50:42.000Z","msg":"歐盟幾個月前講左 不過佢地做野好慢"},{"pid":"93d1e72b024f943b7545312f44a0fd977299a3a7","tid":2508561,"uid":1524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T00:59:16.000Z","msg":"買咗成10年都有<br />\n而家先嚟覺醒<br />\n好過完全唔做嘢嘅"}]}